@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Rejected
Rejected --> Active : process
Active --> Closed : review
Closed --> Created : approve
Created --> Delivered : cancel
Created --> Rejected : revert
Delivered --> [*]
